summary:
Looking to promote the research, analysis and discussion of contemporary architecture developing a unique creative process in which the outcome of combining arts, science and technology will be architectural and construction projects that improve live quality, culture and meaning of society.

Lived and worked in Curacao since 2005 • Creative designer with architectural skills to develop innovative projects • Experienced in working  residential, commercial, cultural and touristic building designs • Experienced in working  landscaping designs • Experienced in mechanical, electrical, plumbing and structural working drawings •Skills developing 3D models, renderings and post production images • Member of DOCOMOMO International • Member of DCAE Dutch Carribean Architects and Engineers • Hobby Architectural Photography • Married • 2 children • Venezuelan and Dutch Nationality/ Passport
